name: The TechNude I
description:
TechNude is a 7 piece collection and it's my first collection. 

This one is TechNude I, the first one of seven. There is nothing here because it looks cool or colorful. Every element has a purpose in it, even unbalanced empty spaces. They have been created for something you have to think of.

About the collection:

There are three main phrases which summarize the collection in a nutshell:

Nudity is the invisible cloth itself.

The Internet gave the power of becoming digital gods to every individual, just like nude Graeco-Roman god statues.

Art itself was a prison for nudity before the Internet.

The collection will include 3 females, 3 males and 1 both. All artworks are already finished and I am working on my third collection now.

Due to restrictions, the writing of the collection and other things are on linktr.ee/LDVinci.

Roadmap:

I will mint 6 pieces of the collection, 7 editions per piece week by week. One week after minting the 6th one, the remaining ones will be burnt. 

The 7th and the last one will be minted in 7 editions but I will send it to the collectors who have all 6 pieces. Of course it will be a present and free. 

Contact info: dedevincileonar@gmail.com

Original file will be sent to the buyers, 4096x3072, 35,97 mb.

See you in another art!
